Class UpdateTagRequest

java.lang.Object
com.FeedEmGreens.HealthyAura.dto.UpdateTagRequest
public class UpdateTagRequest extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) used for updating or renaming a tag associated with an eatery in the database.

This class carries the old tag name and the new tag name that will replace it. It is typically used by the EateryController through the /api/eateries/{eateryId}/tags endpoint.

Example JSON request:

{
  "oldTag": "Vegetarian",
  "newTag": "Plant-Based"
}
